'''科迪·辛普森'''（{{lang-en|Cody Simpson}}，{{bd|1997年|1月11日}}）是一位來自[[澳洲|澳洲]]昆士蘭[[黄金海岸_(澳大利亚)|黄金海岸]]的流行音樂歌手。目前與美國唱片公司[[大西洋唱片|大西洋唱片]]簽約。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.atlanticrecords.com/codysimpson |title=Atlantic Records – Cody Simpson |publisher=atlanticrecords.com |accessdate=15 August 2010 |archive-date=2012-07-22 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120722160235/http://www.atlanticrecords.com/codysimpson |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==早年生活==
辛普森出生於澳洲昆士蘭省黄金海岸。他有2個兄弟姐妹，湯姆（Tom）和阿利（Alli）。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.goldcoast.com.au/article/2010/06/19/229321_news.html|title=The Cody Simpson Effect|last=Grant|first=Dwayne|date=19 June 2010|work=goldcoast.com.au|accessdate=9 August 2010|archive-date=2012-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004081255/http://www.goldcoast.com.au/article/2010/06/19/229321_news.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他同時也是個有才華的游泳運動員，曾在昆士蘭游泳錦標賽上贏得兩枚金牌。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.goldcoast.com.au/article/2009/12/14/169285_gold-coast-sport.html|title=Rickard motivated by loss|last=Dew|first=Jake|date=14 December 2009|work=goldcoast.com.au|accessdate=17 May 2010|archive-date=2012-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004081259/http://www.goldcoast.com.au/article/2009/12/14/169285_gold-coast-sport.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

